SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2011-3 (Matsqui)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2011-3 (MATSQUI) in order to add the name of the Matsqui, the name of its governing body and the description of the lands where Matsqui's goods and services tax law could apply.
